OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Andy Bonner
OL,7,Fspeaking to Lucy Harrison's mother,
OL,8,FJane Coates.
OL,10,FA mother whose daughter was shot dead
OL,11,Fby her father in Texas says her ex-
OL,12,Fhusband was not tested for alcohol or
OL,13,Fdrugs but her daughter's was after her
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
