PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FLucy Harrison, 23, had been staying
OL,7,Fwith her dad, Liverpool-born Kris
OL,8,FHarrison and his family in Prosper,
OL,9,FTexas, when she was shot in the chest
OL,10,Fjust half an hour before she was due
OL,11,Fto leave for the airport for her
OL,12,Fflight home on 10 January 2025.
OL,14,FHer mother, Jane Coates, said
OL,15,Fdetectives told her Lucy had 'died in
OL,16,Fa tragic accident' and that the police
OL,17,Finvestigation was over just six hours
OL,18,Fafter her daughter was shot.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FHer mum said Lucy had everything to
OL,7,Flive for and said she had taught her
OL,8,F'to be a better person'.
OL,10,FShe said the graduate was 'so
OL,11,Fintelligent, funny and was very
OL,12,Fprincipled and had a real moral
OL,13,Fcompass' and was 'passionate in social
OL,14,Fjustice.'
OL,16,FShe had gained a first class honours
OL,17,Fdegree, had a dream job as a fashion
OL,18,Fbuyer and had moved in with her
OL,19,Fpartner Sam on International Women's
OL,20,Fday in March 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FMs Coates said: "Lucy had her whole
OL,7,Flife ahead of her and she had so much
OL,8,Fmore life to live. "
OL,10,F"I take comfort from that she was able
OL,11,Fto experience these things as a young
OL,12,Fadult but it always still very
OL,13,Fpainful."
OL,15,FDescribing the moment a female police
OL,16,Fofficer came to her house in
OL,17,FWarrington, there was still disbelief.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,F"I opened the door, and she just said
OL,7,Fvery ,very clearly there has been a
OL,8,Ftragic accident, Lucy's been shot and
OL,9,Fshe's not made it."
OL,11,F"You'd never expect those words about
OL,12,Fmy daughter, who is British and had
OL,13,Fnever been around guns. It just didn't
OL,14,Fmake sense."
OL,16,F"I never ever thought I wouldn't see
OL,17,Fmy daughter again, because she had
OL,18,Fbeen shot and killed in her dad's home
OL,19,Fin America, somewhere she should have
OL,20,Fbeen safe."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,F"Speaking to the detective, I couldn't
OL,7,Ffathom how on earth they could accept
OL,8,Fthat version of events because the the
OL,9,Finvestigation was over within just six
OL,10,Fhours after Lucy being shot".
OL,12,FA British inquest into Ms Harrison's
OL,13,Fdeath at Cheshire Coroner's Court on
OL,14,FFebruary 12, more than a year after
OL,15,Fher death senior coroner Jacqueline
OL,16,FDevonish ruled she died due to
OL,17,Funlawful killing on the grounds of
OL,18,Fgross negligence manslaughter.
OL,20,FYet in Texas there was no case to
OL,21,Fanswer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FConcluding her inquest Ms Devonish
OL,7,Fsaid: "To shoot her through the chest
OL,8,Fwhile she was standing would have
OL,9,Frequired him to point the gun at his
OL,10,Fdaughter, fail to check for bullets,
OL,11,Fand pull the trigger."
OL,13,F"I find these actions to be reckless."
OL,15,FMr Harrison, described by the coroner
OL,16,Fas a functioning alcoholic, claimed
OL,17,Fthe gun had gone off 'accidentally.'
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@VO]uD@AOUuD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FJane Coates said; "For that trigger to
OL,7,Fhave gone off it had to have been
OL,8,Fpulled, so that means there was an
OL,9,Fintentional decision to pull that
OL,10,Ftrigger, how can that be classed as
OL,11,Faccidental, it just doesn't make
OL,12,Fsense."
OL,14,F"It was very clear to everybody who
OL,15,Fwas close to Lucy how she felt about
OL,16,Fher dad having a gun in the house."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FJane says she understands the cultural
OL,7,Fdifferences, in the UK and US where
OL,8,Fgun ownership is seen as a fundamental
OL,9,Fright, and believes those attitudes
OL,10,Finfluenced officers.
OL,12,F"I really do believe Kris wanted Lucy
OL,13,Fto see that gun, I don't know why he
OL,14,Ffelt that was so important. He had
OL,15,Falcohol and he felt bold and that was
OL,16,Fsomething he wanted to do."
OL,18,F"I do believe certain attitudes
OL,19,Faffected choices and decisions that
OL,20,Fwere made by the Prosper police in
OL,21,FTexas."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FShe believes her ex-husband should
OL,7,Fhave been more aware of the dangerous
OL,8,Fnature of the weapon, a Glock semi-
OL,9,Fautomatic handgun, which he kept
OL,10,Flocked inside a box in his bedside
OL,11,Fcabinet.
OL,13,F"I don't believe he intentionally
OL,14,Fmeant to kill his daughter," Ms Coates
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,F"I accept the coroner said she
OL,7,Faccepted that he wasn't aware there
OL,8,Fwas a loaded bullet in the chamber.
OL,9,FBut my point is, he should have been
OL,10,Faware, and it's an incredibly
OL,11,Fdangerous weapon."
OL,13,FJane Coates said she will do
OL,14,Feverything she can to give her
OL,15,Fdaughter a voice, and feels the
OL,16,Finvestigation in America failed her
OL,17,Fand she does not want another family
OL,18,Fto go through the trauma they have
OL,19,Fsuffered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,FMs Coates wants her daughter's case
OL,7,Freopened and she's calling on the
OL,8,FForeign Office to offer more support
OL,9,Fwhen a British national dies in
OL,10,Funnatural circumstances.
OL,12,F"Even though Lucy was killed in
OL,13,Fanother country, yet it felt like
OL,14,Fsorry, it's happened over there we
OL,15,Fcan't do anything."
OL,17,F"It was not good enough and in your
OL,18,Fmoment of deepest confusion, grief and
OL,19,Fshock, you need an advocate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775153467
OL,3,CMother says father who shot daughter
OL,4,Cin Texas can still legally own a gun
OL,6,F"But I felt totally and utterly
OL,7,Fabandoned."
OL,9,FShe said she understands her ex-
OL,10,Fhusband can still own a gun for self
OL,11,Fdefence because there was no
OL,12,Fprosecution and she asks how can that
OL,13,Fbe justice?
OL,15,FThe FCO have been approached for
OL,16,Fcomment.
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
